    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable given the device class, model influence level, and decision consequence profile. Validation results for pressure-flow and hemolysis index demonstrate adequate predictive accuracy (E_rel < 10%) across all COU operating points. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion is satisfied with margin. The package is accepted for regulatory submission supporting the CPB device 510(k) submission.",
